      • CkanResource

        public CkanResource(String format,
            String name,
            String url,
            String description,
            String packageId,
            String mimetype)
        Constructor with the minimal list of required items to successfully create a resource on the server.
        Parameters:
        format - i.e. file format in capital letters, i.e. "CSV"
        name - resource name, i.e. "My Cool resource"
        url - the Url to the pyhsical file, i.e. http://dati.trentino.it/storage/f/2013-05-09T140831/TRENTO_Laghi_monitorati_UTM.csv
        description -
        packageId - id of the dataset that contains the resource
        mimetype -
